Requirements:

Raspberry Pi
WiringPi
Mplayer
Fbi
FBTFT

Toggling GPIO2 makes the video move up one frame at a time. Toggling GPIO3 makes the video move down one frame at a time. Feed back the CS signal into GPIO23

To install:
make install

pristitrope-daemon is installed as a service (in /etc/init.d)
asplashscreen is also installed as a service